Package: arschooldata
Title: Arkansas School Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A simple, consistent interface for accessing Arkansas
    school data from the Arkansas Division of Elementary and Secondary
    Education (DESE). Provides functions for fetching enrollment data from
    Annual Statistical Reports, which contain Average Daily Attendance (ADA)
    and fiscal information for Arkansas school districts.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
